{"tid":625584,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"一人N個爭啲死既經歷","createTime":"2018-04-11T14:43:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-14T00:38:15.000Z","uid":171594,"like":1,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"6a971ea032b9003326ad803ca2e405923cc8bf74","tid":625584,"uid":171594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T14:43:27.000Z","msg":"試過同fd一路行一路傾計<br />\n過對面馬路要過兩盞紅綠燈<br />\n過咗第一盞停係度繼續傾<br />\n冇為意前面<br />\n聽到轉燈就諗住行<br />\n個fd即刻拉住我<br />\n同時有架車係我身邊快速經過<br />\n原來我係聽到後面盞燈轉咗<br />\n前面盞燈未轉<br />\n我個陣再行前多步就係咁先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n死亡真係可以離我地好近<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8d957756c13162fb68b8027edebd3400dedc674","tid":625584,"uid":24310,"like":47,"dislike":3,"score":44,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T14:48:01.000Z","msg":"同幾億兄弟一齊游水<br />\n得我仲生存緊<br />\n差d死"},{"pid":"bc5395fcf0878a2a87801407f2122193d4162db0","tid":625584,"uid":170044,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T14:49:15.000Z","msg":"係山上面食煙"},{"pid":"4a0c49144a9046d18890ead944da3ff65346bcf8","tid":625584,"uid":5077,"like":3,"dislike":34,"score":-31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T14:49:18.000Z","msg":"中學去grad trip嗰陣，<br />\n有幾條女同時都暗戀緊我，<br />\n佢地就搵晚入晒我間房撩我做愛，<br />\n佢地幾個一齊服侍緊我嗰陣真係爽到升天咁，<br />\n個心臟跳得勁快，仲跳到有啲痛，<br />\n成個人已經郁唔到咁訓咗喺到，<br />\n佢地仲以為我enjoy緊，<br />\n更加俾多兩錢肉緊，<br />\n有個直程騎埋上嚟自動波咁un，<br />\n另外兩個又不甘示弱咁，<br />\n又奶我lin頭又同我打茄輪"},{"pid":"2e6a481285b65f395a033b8a14ec0b6f5bd3561c","tid":625584,"uid":177947,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T15:51:27.000Z","msg":"細個同屋企人去泰國沙灘玩<br />\n自己一個貪大海咁出咗海玩浪 啲水都浸到上塊面到 <br />\n點知想上翻水嗰時啲水流係咁拉住我 行前兩步又拉翻我出海 卡咗喺度成幾分鐘 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n最後等到啲水流完咗先上到岸<br />\n同我呀媽講翻先發現原來大把人就係咁俾海水流走咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我連自己差啲死都唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c1be4eb5987e8cb0f148ab2a8ec633ca75471ed","tid":625584,"uid":177947,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"2e6a481285b65f395a033b8a14ec0b6f5bd3561c","tid":625584,"uid":177947,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T15:51:27.000Z","msg":"細個同屋企人去泰國沙灘玩<br />\n自己一個貪大海咁出咗海玩浪 啲水都浸到上塊面到 <br />\n點知想上翻水嗰時啲水流係咁拉住我 行前兩步又拉翻我出海 卡咗喺度成幾分鐘 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n最後等到啲水流完咗先上到岸<br />\n同我呀媽講翻先發現原來大把人就係咁俾海水流走咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我連自己差啲死都唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T15:52:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">沖</span></span>"},{"pid":"a0482a2c019884e767b9864a70d4ee44d02c3c7d","tid":625584,"uid":175108,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T19:23:52.000Z","msg":"坐雪橇滑雪(果啲膠兜仔)<br />\n不受控制向前衝<br />\n刹掣拉左都冇用<br />\n一直衝向山崖邊<br />\n好彩臨跌前俾人一手拖左落橇"},{"pid":"38caba95177e2c5288264f40cfab39d03f9ce8f9","tid":625584,"uid":34023,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T19:43:17.000Z","msg":"過馬路<br />\n仲係綠公仔<br />\n點知pass過咗第一條行車線之後，第二條線架私家車直衝<br />\n好在我過馬路習慣望住啲車<br />\n如果唔係停慢一步都車死<br />\n之後我望一望confirm仲係綠公仔，然後望一望第一線等轉燈架van仔<br />\n成車人都望住我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n屌佢老母盲撚司機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad890cc0a31c1bbaf16a411ed1daba1b8452cf55","tid":625584,"uid":177449,"like":13,"dislike"